Spectra Cyber INSTALL
==============

You must have CMake >= 2.4.7 in order to build this package.

1) $ tar -xzf indi-spectracyber.tar.gz
2) $ mkdir indi-spectracyber_build
3) $ cd indi-spectracyber_build
4) $ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr . ../indi-spectracyber
5) $ su -c 'make install' or sudo make install
   
Refer to README for instructions on using the driver.

That's it!

